  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink107">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>aṉṉai vāḻivēṇ ṭaṉṉaiyeṉ ṟōḻi</l>
<l>cuṭarnutal pacappac cāayp paṭarmelintu</l>
<l>taṇkaṭaṟ paṭutirai kēṭṭoṟun</l>
<l>tuñcā ḷākuta ṉōkō yāṉē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>  Oh mother, please mother,</l>
<l>As my friend's bright forehead becomes pale,</l>
<l>Having faded, [and she] becoming weak [due to her] affliction,</l>
<l>I am indeed hurt</l>
<l>[Because of her] becoming one who does not sleep</l>
<l>Every time she hears the crashing waves of the cool ocean.</l>
</lg>
